        "ggC_kKO9rgD_text": "<p>Table of Contents</p>",
        "ggCzXY_IT0i_text": "<p><a href=\"https://www.procolored.com/blogs/news/dtg-printing-101-the-top-10-faqs\" target=\"_blank\">DTG Printing 101: The Top 10 FAQs</a></p>",
        "ggE0cGiBi_9_text": "<p>Changing your way of doing business to <a href=\"https://www.procolored.com/collections/dtg-printer\" target=\"_blank\"><u>DTG printing</u></a> doesn’t just update the workflow, it completely redefines how your business operates. Here is how:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>● Economies of Scale:</strong> Instead of tying up funds on racks of pre-printed designs, you only keep blank garments and print only what sells. This leads to less deadstock and more positive cash flow. Those red clearance bins full of “missed trends” will be a thing of the past.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>● Reduction of Lead Times:</strong> What used to take weeks for approvals and screen-sets and bulk runs—can now be turned around in mere hours. Customers get their orders at a much more reasonable time now which means a quicker payment for you as well.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>● Simplified Workflow:</strong> The steps are super simple and direct—the user has to upload a file, run the file through RIP, print it, cure it, and let it dry. There are a reduced amount of steps which leads to a lesser chance of making an error, all while being less stressed and having the ability to scale.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>● Shift in the Labor Skills Needed:</strong> There is no need for screen printing, which used to require many people. The only thing your staff has to do and focus on now are the digital skills of coloring prep and finishing. This is no longer manual work, it is now much more about exercising creative control.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>● Quality Control:</strong> Need to test a design? Instead of going through the annoyingly tedious and long printing processes, simply try to roll out a single sample first, and then make adjustments afterwards to the bulk. Guesswork is eliminated, and you now have a tighter control workflow before large orders get printed.</p><p>The ability to adapt to changing market norms and customer needs is no longer a phenomenal advantage but a necessity for businesses. This process allows improvement in productivity as well, in addition to greater flexibility.</p>",
        "ggEtmIfWUum_text": "<p>Every time a customer puts on a DTG printed shirt, it’s not simply a piece of clothing, it’s an immersed experience with your brand. This is how <a href=\"https://www.procolored.com/collections/dtg-printer\" target=\"_blank\"><u>DTG printing</u></a> machine enhances the experience:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>● Artwork Taken To A Whole New Level:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.procolored.com/collections/dtg-printer\" target=\"_blank\"><u>DTG printers</u></a> doesn’t simply print an image, it photographs it. With photographic level detail, DTG captures moods, gradience, tiny brush strokes and designs. So the shirt captures the essence of wearable art. The ink added to the shirt merges with the fabric of the shirt keeping it soft and not plasticky.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>● Keepsakes, Not Just Clothing:</strong> DTG printers simplify the art of personalization. Items such as a birthday shirt with a name, a wedding shirt with a date or a shirt with a hyper local inside joke become personal keepsakes.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>● Luxury Without a Markup:</strong> The luxury of printing on high-thread-count cotton will sit your designs on high quality fabric. This will result in boutique ready shirts which gives you the opportunity to set higher prices, all while your customers will feel as though they are getting an amazing deal.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And this is how Procolored DTG printers elevate it. Their unparalleled white ink technology allows dark and light garments to glow with the same brightness. Plus, colors match every single print, so no one’s getting a washed-out mess on a reorder..This doesn’t just make a huge technical difference, but transforms one time customer to a lifetime customer.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Not only is Procolored DTG printers able to print quality garments, but along with that, the experience they deliver is top tier.</p>",
        "ggJDFv88CAq_text": "<p>More Blogs About</p>",
        "ggKQcmm3ScK_text": "<p><a href=\"#gBaAJwGhKU\"><strong>1. Operational Transformation: Real, Measurable Changes</strong></a></p><p><a href=\"#g4p7b77eNR\"><strong>2. Product &amp; Customer Value</strong></a></p><p><a href=\"#grR8PUIYot\"><strong>3. Marketing &amp; Sales Edge</strong></a></p><p><a href=\"#gQtm4-eBQK\"><strong>4. Financial Transformation</strong></a></p><p><a href=\"#ghojsnakAb\"><strong>5. Implementation Roadmap</strong></a></p><p><a href=\"#gG1Kf74Him\"><strong>6. Common Objections + Concise Rebuttals</strong></a></p><p><a href=\"#goEvqsLngo\"><strong>7. Growth and Scale Strategies</strong></a></p><p><a href=\"#gpBWiupaIH\"><strong>8. Closing Thoughts: Quick Action Steps</strong></a></p>",
        "ggLboDUr1B__text": "<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong>Implementation Roadmap</strong></span>",
