        "ggoCa0Ce-SN_text": "<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong>Product &amp; Customer Value</strong></span>",
        "ggoFsFMFBJ1_text": "<p>Stop just daydreaming about making your clothing brand pop off—actually take the steps that get you ahead. Honestly, with Procolored <a href=\"https://www.procolored.com/collections/dtg-printer\" target=\"_blank\"><u>DTG printers</u></a> in your space, every little move translates into progress.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>● Print your premium sample today and photograph it</strong></p><p>Your finest creation is sample proof and validation of what you can offer.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>● Create+Launch a “Design + Print” product.</strong></p><p>One polished product image communicates to your customers that you have just commenced your business activity.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>● Reach out to one boutique or event organizer.</strong></p><p>A positive response from one of the collaborators can lead to a reliable source of new orders.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The sample, show, and share strategy is proven. Start with these 3, and with Procolored, you can convert minor prints to great successes.</p>",
